  "original_title": "Litro to supply gas only for essential services",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Litro to supply gas only for essential services",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Litro Gas says that the supply of LP gas will continue only for essential services.",
        "Its Chairman, Muditha Peiris stated that domestic gas cylinders will not be released to the market until 7th July.",
        "He also said that steps have been taken to import 33,000 metric tons of LP gas within July.",
        "Accordingly, the relevant shipment is scheduled to reach the island on 6th July."
      ],
